<doc id="761438" wikidata="Q1072943" url="?curid=761438" title="Clione">
<text>Clione is a genus of small, floating sea slugs, pelagic marine gastropod mollusks in the family Clionidae, the sea angels.

&quot;Clione&quot; is the type genus of the family Clionidae.

== Species ==
Species within the genus &quot;Clione&quot; include:
*&quot;Clione antarctica&quot; 
*&quot;Clione elegantissima&quot; 
*&quot;Clione limacina&quot; 
*&quot;Clione okhotensis&quot; 

